{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/manifests/herbert-huncke-at-ultimatum-festival-1985-05-05.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"en":["Herbert Huncke at Ultimatum Festival 1985-05-05"]},"homepage":[{"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985","type":"Text","label":{"en":["Herbert Huncke at Ultimatum Festival 1985-05-05"]},"format":"text/html"}],"metadata":[{"label":{"en":["Description"]},"value":{"en":["The following is a transcription of the Herbert Huncke set at Ultimatum, Sunday, May 5th, 1985 at the Foufounes Electriques. Huncke was an American writer and poet and member of the Beat Generation, a term which he is considered to have coined. He is the author of the book The Evening Sun Turned Crimson from which he reads three stories in his Ultimatum set: \"Cuba\", \"Alvarez\", and \"Russian Blackie\"."]}},{"label":{"en":["Language"]},"value":{"en":["English"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7","type":"Canvas","duration":2495,"annotations":[{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/manifests/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05-canvas7-1","type":"AnnotationPage","label":{"en":["Default"]},"items":[{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Applause.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=0,6"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"J’espere, j’espere un jour que on peut dire 'Herbert Huncke' puis on l’appreciera pleinement son avoir a faire des deferences a la Beat Generation, Kerouac, Ginsberg, Burroughs, tous ca. Maintenant je la fait une derniere fois, la prochaine fois c’est Herbert Huncke, tout seul.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Alan Lord","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=6,25"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Alright!","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience Member","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=25,25"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Applause and cheers.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=25,29"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Okay, well let me just say first before we start, all, what has happened this evening [unintelligible] a hard act to follow [unintelligible] oh well, alright, in the mic he says. Okay, can you hear now? Yes. See I have a problem with this lighting situation here, regardless of all that. I lost my place. How do you like that?","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=29,59"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"You have to talk into the mic.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Unknown Speaker","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=59,61"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"I will in just a minute. Some people can hear me though.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=61,64"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Chatter.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=64,67"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Are you satisfied now? Okay. I really wanna start off with one particular story here because I feel that it will fit into the general theme of the so-called gathering or festival whatever, group of creative people doing things, trying to do things, young people. It’s very very encouraging for an old man like me, you know I want to think that things have progressed [laughs] a little. Boy.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=67,115"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Laughter.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=115,117"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Well, here, I wasn’t gonna read this one, but I will. I’ll start anyway so everything is under control. It’s called \"Cuba\". It’s a rather strange story in that the individual involved was someone I met and felt somewhat sorry for if I may be permitted to feel sorry about anybody.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=117,139"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Reads \"Cuba\" from The Evening Sun Turned Crimson [brief moments of laughter throughout].","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=139,575"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Applause.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=575,579"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Sorry, it’s not the one I want, oh I can’t do it now [unintelligible].","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=579,583"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Applause.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=583,587"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Thank you [off mic], let me see if I can find the one I intended to start out with. \"Alvarez\". One, let’s see, one fifty one, okay, we’ll get there, hell or high water [laughs], ah, there [laughs]. This is a, I feel it’s a very, very sad story mysel - woops. \"Alvarez\".","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=587,614"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Reads \"Alvarez\" from The Evening Sun Turned Crimson.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=614,649"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Cuts out, light static.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Recording","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=649,651"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Silence.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Recording","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7#t=651,652"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/herbert_huncke_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/7/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Continues reading.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Herbert Huncke","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motiv